{"tid":2302154,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人返工做唔到野／做衰咗會好驚","createTime":"2020-11-27T01:55:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-28T14:42:57.000Z","uid":192883,"like":35,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"2403500e88ab84facf05d1a11e36c08f10e7c98f","tid":2302154,"uid":192883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T01:55:21.000Z","msg":"首先小弟係做工程乾收銀，返咗大概三個月到，就黎過試用。但幾乎次次做野都表現好差<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，唔係次次做完都有手尾俾人跟，就係做得唔掂／大佬唔收貨，要等其他人接手。雖然重未去到真係俾人開口屌的地步。但個內心始終好驚。有時搞到d同事收唔到工都會唸佢地內心會唔會都好憎我／屌緊我。或者唸大佬會唔會終有一日頂唔順而炒咗我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />搞到依家內心真係好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然每次都好努力想做番好d，但最尾都係衰。依家係到唸我其實係咪唔適合做工程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。而且最近收到aco skill test email(係我收呢份工offer之前報）。定係我應該放棄工程，走去同dse生爭aco算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2d7d0363f74a47033b8e24b68c1e2e4472fee89","tid":2302154,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T02:04:40.000Z","msg":"試下aco啦"},{"pid":"7d4f542d7055bd111fcde8b4353ce9e088d1d846","tid":2302154,"uid":229342,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T02:13:24.000Z","msg":"u grad定i大grad?  有無行scheme"},{"pid":"82b3cf166ddcf30c025b26eaaab49689028b70ae","tid":2302154,"uid":192883,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"7d4f542d7055bd111fcde8b4353ce9e088d1d846","tid":2302154,"uid":229342,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T02:13:24.000Z","msg":"u grad定i大grad?  有無行scheme"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T02:20:22.000Z","msg":"u grad<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n未行scheme，但過完試用會問你行唔行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dbb8c00bd842b5627cb2bd906c90bdd4fee6b4d","tid":2302154,"uid":192883,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"a2d7d0363f